<body>
<div id="introOverlay" class="intro-overlay">
    <div class="intro-card">
        <h1>🏮 同福客栈 · 入境审查 🏮</h1>
        <p>欢迎，同福客栈的伙计！今日起你受佟掌柜指派，在七侠镇关口盘查来往江湖人士。必须核对「口供」与「通关文牒」是否吻合，谨防奸细、骗子与不速之客。</p>
        <p>📜 六大核对法则（缺一不可）：</p>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ 姓名一致</li>
            <li>✅ 江湖ID一致</li>
            <li>✅ 相貌描述一致</li>
            <li>✅ 暗号指纹一致</li>
            <li>✅ 文牒有效期 ≥ 今日</li>
            <li>✅ 签发地 = 七侠镇 (同福管辖)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>⚡ 随机事件考验你的情商与底线，每个选择都可能引来后续剧情！完成30件案子（6天任期），根据表现获得不同结局和武林外传专属成就。</p>
        <p>🎭 你可能是：佟湘玉、白展堂、郭芙蓉、吕秀才、李大嘴…… 看命运安排！</p>
        <button class="start-btn" id="startGameBtn">✨ 走你 ✨</button>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="game-container" id="gameContainer" style="display: none;">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="officer-info">🛂 今日值班 · <span id="officerName" class="officer-name">--</span></div>
        <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat"><span>🍜 声誉值</span> <span id="scoreValue">0</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><span>💰 私房钱</span> <span id="moneyValue">0</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><span>📌 已查案件</span> <span id="caseCounter">0</span><span id="totalCasesSpan">/0</span></div>
            <div class="day-info" id="dayInfo">第 1 / 6 日</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rule-panel">
        <ul class="rule-list">
            <li>✅ 姓名一致</li><li>✅ 江湖ID一致</li><li>✅ 相貌描述一致</li>
            <li>✅ 暗号/指纹一致</li><li>✅ 文牒有效期 ≥ 今日</li><li>✅ 签发地 = 七侠镇</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="date-badge">📅 标准日: 乙酉年 腊月廿三</div>
    </div>
    <div id="dailyEffectArea" class="daily-effect" style="display: none;"></div>
    <div id="decreeWarning" class="decree-warning" style="display: none; text-align: center; margin: 8px 20px;"></div>
    <div id="dynamicEventArea" class="event-area" style="display: none;"></div>

    <div class="inspection-area">
        <div style="text-align:center;"><span class="applicant-title">✧ 江湖客·口供 vs 通关文牒 ✧</span></div>
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🗣️ 口 头 声 明</h3>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">姓名</span><span class="info-value" id="declName">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">江湖ID</span><span class="info-value" id="declID">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">相貌描述</span><span class="info-value" id="declPhoto">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">暗号指纹</span><span class="info-value" id="declFinger">—</span></div>
                <div class="warning-note">⚠️ 此人自称如是说</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>📜 通 关 文 牒</h3>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">姓名</span><span class="info-value" id="docName">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">江湖ID</span><span class="info-value" id="docID">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">相貌描述</span><span class="info-value" id="docPhoto">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">暗号指纹</span><span class="info-value" id="docFinger">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">文牒有效期</span><span class="info-value" id="docExpiry">—</span></div>
                <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">签发地</span><span class="info-value" id="docIssue">—</span></div>
                <div class="warning-note">🔍 必须全部匹配六项法则</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-area">
        <button class="approve-btn" id="approveBtn">✅ 准 入</button>
        <button class="reject-btn" id="rejectBtn">⛔ 拒 之 门 外</button>
    </div>

    <div class="item-area" id="itemArea">
        <span class="item">🛡️ 免罪护符: <span id="amuletCount">0</span></span>
        <span class="item">🔍 盗圣放大镜: <span id="lensCount">0</span>次</span>
        <span class="item">💰 贿赂豁免券: <span id="bribeExemptCount">0</span></span>
    </div>

    <div class="feedback" id="feedbackMsg">静待江湖客，同福有规矩。</div>
    <div class="bottom-bar">
        <button class="reset-btn" id="resetBtn">🔄 重开江湖</button>
        <button class="shop-btn" id="shopBtn">🏪 老白私货铺</button>
    </div>
    <footer>六天任期·三十件案子·事件后续皆有因果·额滴神啊，认真点！</footer>
</div>

<div id="shopModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <h3>🏪 白展堂私货小摊</h3>
        <div class="shop-item">🛡️ 免罪护符 <span>抵消一次错误扣分</span> <button id="buyAmulet">买 (30💰)</button></div>
        <div class="shop-item">🔍 盗圣放大镜 <span>每案提示一条疑点 (3次/份)</span> <button id="buyLens">买 (20💰)</button></div>
        <div class="shop-item">💰 贿赂豁免券 <span>下次受贿不扣声誉</span> <button id="buyExempt">买 (40💰)</button></div>
        <button class="close-modal" id="closeModal">关门放小郭</button>
    </div>
</div>

